Very thin material,

238
00:13:37,686 --> 00:13:41,991
the helium goes up,
reflects against the top,

239
00:13:41,991 --> 00:13:45,222
is pushed back again,
you get this peculiar mushroom

240
00:13:45,222 --> 00:13:48,137
shape, it makes an enormous
sound like a storm.

241
00:13:48,137 --> 00:13:51,369
The idea now is that this
balloon will go higher and

242
00:13:51,369 --> 00:13:54,22
higher in the sky.
Will pick up all this empty

243
00:13:54,22 --> 00:13:55,868
part.
This is not inflated.

244
00:13:55,868 --> 00:13:59,353
As the balloon goes up in the
atmosphere the atmospheric

245
00:13:59,353 --> 00:14:02,648
pressure will go down.
And the helium will expand and

246
00:14:02,648 --> 00:14:06,007
