And the -- the trick now is for

247
00:14:06,007 --> 00:14:09,428
this truck to manipulate,
to maneuver itself under what

248
00:14:09,428 --> 00:14:11,977
we
call the bubble.

249
00:14:11,977 --> 00:14:16,379
And therefore the wind has to
be in this direction so that the

250
00:14:16,379 --> 00:14:20,564
