00:23:35,177 --> 00:23:38,733
animals are completely harmless,
why don't you go first.

425
00:23:38,733 --> 00:23:42,483
This animal was no farther than
four feet from the payload.

426
00:23:42,483 --> 00:23:46,426
And so my graduate student went
first and the amazing thing is

427
00:23:46,426 --> 00:23:50,176
during the ten hours that it
took us to recover the payload

428
00:23:50,176 --> 00:23:53,732
and put it back on Jack's truck
