429
00:23:53,732 --> 00:23:57,481
It was just sitting there
completely still.

430
00:23:57,481 --> 00:24:00,473
This is their way of trying not
to be noticed.

431
00:24:00,473 --> 00:24:02,533
And so here you see the
payload.

432
00:24:02,533 --> 00:24:04,593
This was Alice,
was Jack's wife,

433
00:24:04,593 --> 00:24:07,917
this is Tom Brooks,
he came from the United States,

434
00:24:07,917 --> 00:24:11,705
he was an electronic expert.
