00:25:26,611 --> 00:25:32,832
nineteen eighty.
Many from the United States.

457
00:25:32,832 --> 00:25:35,405
From Canada and also from
Australia.

458
00:25:35,405 --> 00:25:39,595
Where that's a s- southern
